OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FStormont's Finance Minister has called
OL,8,Ffor direct support from the Government
OL,9,Fto people in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fstruggling with the rise in the cost
OL,11,Fof home heating oil following the
OL,12,Fstart of war in the Middle East.
OL,14,FJohn O'Dowd said the power sharing
OL,15,FExecutive does not have the financial
OL,16,F"firepower" to fund any relief scheme.
OL,18,FThe minister said he believed the cost
OL,19,Fof any such initiative could run into
OL,20,Fhundreds of millions of pounds.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has already
OL,8,Facknowledged the "unique issues"
OL,9,Faround heating oil, which is used by
OL,10,Faround two thirds of domestic
OL,11,Fproperties in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FGlobal oil prices have risen sharply
OL,14,Fin response to the crisis in the
OL,15,FMiddle East, with Iran launching
OL,16,Fstrikes in response to attacks by the
OL,17,FUS and Israel.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FThe Consumer Council said the average
OL,8,Fprice of 500 litres of home heating
OL,9,Foil in Northern Ireland saw an 81%
OL,10,Fincrease in a week after the start of
OL,11,Fthe conflict.
OL,13,FThe heating oil market in Northern
OL,14,FIreland is unregulated, unlike gas and
OL,15,Felectricity.
OL,17,FTreasury minister Lord Livermore is
OL,18,Fmeeting with MPs, including some from
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland, on Wednesday to
OL,20,Fdiscuss the issues.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FMr O'Dowd said he had written to the
OL,8,FChief Secretary to the Treasury James
OL,9,FMurray to ask for direct engagement
OL,10,Fwith the Stormont Executive.
OL,12,FHe said: "The Executive is best placed
OL,13,Fto represent the people here and put
OL,14,Facross the case for supported
OL,15,Finterventions in that matter.
OL,26,@tD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"The Minister for the Economy (Caoimhe
OL,8,FArchibald) has also been in regular
OL,9,Fcontact with ministers both in London
OL,10,Fand Dublin in relation to the ongoing
OL,11,Fenergy crisis and the call for direct
OL,12,Fintervention from the British
OL,13,FGovernment in relation to support for
OL,14,Fbusinesses and homeowners here in
OL,15,Frelation to the ongoing crisis in
OL,16,Frelation to the significantly rising
OL,17,Fcost of home heating oil.
OL,19,F"We will continue that engagement, it
OL,20,Fis vitally important that that support
OL,21,Fcomes from Westminster.
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"The Executive simply does not have
OL,8,Fthe ability to intervene at the scale
OL,9,Fof challenges that are being faced at
OL,10,Fthis stage."
OL,12,FMr O'Dowd said he believed a relief
OL,13,Fscheme was necessary and that it is
OL,14,Fthe "responsibility of the British
OL,15,FGovernment to fund that scheme".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@LO]vD@EOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FResponding to remarks by US President
OL,8,FDonald Trump that the war in Iran
OL,9,Fcould soon end, the minister said: "I
OL,10,Fhope for humanitarian reasons that the
OL,11,Fwar in Iran is coming to an end and
OL,12,Fthe people who are suffering there,
OL,13,Fthat suffering is brought to an end
OL,14,Fimmediately.
OL,16,F"I think the consequences of what has
OL,17,Fhappened over this last week to 10
OL,18,Fdays will continue to reverberate
OL,19,Facross economies for many months to
OL,20,Fcome.
OL,26,@qD@dOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"People right here are facing the
OL,8,Fconsequences, particularly of rising
OL,9,Fhome heating oil costs and that needs
OL,10,Fto be dealt with."
OL,12,FMr O'Dowd said similar schemes had
OL,13,Fbeen rolled out in the past.
OL,15,FHe said: "In terms of the scale of
OL,16,Fcosts involved, the Executive simply
OL,17,Fdoesn't have that firepower, we are
OL,18,Flooking towards the British Government.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@RO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"I think there needs to be a unified
OL,8,Fvoice from this place (Stormont) in
OL,9,Frelation towards looking towards the
OL,10,FBritish Government to fund that
OL,11,Fscheme."
OL,13,FAsked about the potential cost of such
OL,14,Fa scheme, Mr O'Dowd said: "It could be
OL,15,Finto the hundreds of millions of
OL,16,Fpounds, the Executive doesn't have
OL,17,Fthat sort of cash available to it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]vD@[OUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
