PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FWhile the cost of oil has come down
OL,8,Fover the last 24 hours, it is still
OL,9,Fsitting a lot higher than pre-war
OL,10,Flevels.
OL,12,FThrowing public money at heating oil
OL,13,Fprice spikes 'not the solution'
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has said that
OL,16,Fusing public money to tackle spikes in
OL,17,Fheating oil prices is "not the
OL,18,Fsolution".
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FDomestic heating oil, which is used to
OL,8,Fwarm around 1.5 million UK homes `
OL,9,Fapproximately 5% ` has seen its prices
OL,10,Frise dramatically amid the crisis in
OL,11,Fthe Middle East.
OL,13,FAfter Iran launched strikes across the
OL,14,Fregion in response to attacks from the
OL,15,FUS and Israel, there have been fears
OL,16,Fof a lengthy disruption to the supply
OL,17,Fof oil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FPeople using heating oil are
OL,8,Fparticularly vulnerable to such
OL,9,Fshocks, because there is no cap to
OL,10,Flimit the cost of heating oil in the
OL,11,Fway households benefit from regulator
OL,12,FOfgem's price cap on gas and
OL,13,Felectricity bills.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor has acknowledged the
OL,16,F"unique issues" around heating oil,
OL,17,Fwhich particularly impacts rural
OL,18,Fcommunities and Northern Ireland,
OL,19,Fwhere 60% of households use heating
OL,20,Foil.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FTreasury minister Lord Livermore is
OL,8,Fmeeting with MPs on Wednesday to
OL,9,Fdiscuss the issues.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Ms Reeves has asked the
OL,12,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) to look at the cost of heating
OL,14,Foil, as well as fuel pump prices, to
OL,15,Fprevent price gouging.
OL,17,FBut Ms Reeves has indicated that she
OL,18,Fwill not be providing any relief to
OL,19,Fheating oil customers with public
OL,20,Ffunds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,FHer comments came after Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrat energy spokesperson Pippa
OL,9,FHeylings called on the Government to
OL,10,Fintroduce three months of zero rating
OL,11,Ffor VAT on heating oil.
OL,13,FDuring Treasury questions in the
OL,14,FCommons, Ms Heylings said: "In my
OL,15,Fconstituency of South Cambridgeshire,
OL,16,Fas we've heard from constituencies
OL,17,Faround the chamber, there are many
OL,18,Frural and semi-rural households who
OL,19,Fhave to use oil for heating and over
OL,20,Fthe last week have seen those prices
OL,21,Fdouble.
OL,26,@vD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"I've heard the Chancellor is
OL,8,Fconsidering potential measures to
OL,9,Fsupport them.
OL,11,F"Will she support the Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats' three months zero rating
OL,13,Ffor VAT on heating oil for all of
OL,14,Fthose residential homes, and other
OL,15,Fmeasures to protect them from these
OL,16,Fjust massive spikes and impact on
OL,17,Ftheir bills?"
OL,19,FResponding, the Chancellor said:
OL,20,F"There's two things going on in terms
OL,21,Fof heating oil.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@MO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"First of all, you've got the conflict
OL,8,Fin the Middle East, which we're trying
OL,9,Fto de-escalate.
OL,11,F"And second, you've got price gouging,
OL,12,Fand the way to deal with that is to
OL,13,Fensure that customers are treated
OL,14,Ffairly and that companies are not
OL,15,Fripping off their customers.
OL,17,F"That is why we've asked the CMA to
OL,18,Flook at the issues around heating oil.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773249076
OL,3,CO'Dowd calls for direct support for
OL,4,Ccustomers hit by home heating oil
OL,5,Cprice rise
OL,7,F"But we've got to get to the root of
OL,8,Fthe problem, which is that vessels
OL,9,Faren't flowing through the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz and some businesses are using
OL,11,Fthis crisis as an opportunity to rip
OL,12,Foff consumers.
OL,14,F"Let's deal with that, rather than
OL,15,Fthrowing public money at something
OL,16,Fwhich is not the solution ` price
OL,17,Fgouging and getting oil flowing is."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/18
